data.description: PERFECT opportunity to own your home in the heart of Magalia! This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom homes offers spacious living areas and has a few exciting updates! These updates include newer floors and updated electrical! All appliances in the home are staying for the buyer! Cozy up next to the wood burning stove on those cool nights or enjoy the cental heating & air! Both bedrooms are large and offer great closet space. This home sits away from the street offering a spacious front yard, but also has a backyard. Relax in the mornings on your huge front deck, or BBQ in the evenings on your back porch! Garage is large with high ceilings which gives you enough space for an engine hoist! The Paradise Pines Property Owners Association is within walking distance and offers a ton of amenities such as an Olympic sized pool, huge hot tub, exclusive bar, tennis courts, bocce ball court, playground, and more! Come view this beauty today and claim this home as your own!
